data.name: description.Text
data.value: A trio of vibrant yellow tulip bulbs, arranged together in our classic cream wrapping. Make even the most mundane of days thrice as magical, with our sweet, simple & sublime Adelyn floral arrangement.

data.name: description3.Text
data.value: Indulge in the pinkest of moments through this sweet-looking creation. Its soft colours paired with beautiful petals make for a pleasant feeling like no other, ideal for any space you could think of.

data.name: description4.Text
data.value: Golden like the sun, with rich hues of amber medleyed in between - our Meliora flower bouquet is a gleaming gift, made to convey sincere love, care & affection. Starring a vibrant sunflower, surrounded by bright bulbs of tulip blooms - this arrangement is perfect for adding a touch of sweet sunshine to just about anyone's day.

data.name: description2.Text
data.value: Ravishing pops of red, vibrant yellow hues, and gleaming sparkles of white - arranged together to bring you our gorgeous Andromeda flower bouquet. Starring the classic red rose, paired together with ethereal bulbs of tulip & aster blooms - this alluring arrangement is perfect for conveying your unbound love & passion.
